			<div type="bibliography">
				<p>First reported in <bibl><ptr target="bib:ASI"/><citedRange>1928-29: 108</citedRange></bibl>, as a statue minus its head with the “Buddhist formula” in Sanskrit round the base. <bibl><ptr target="bib:MonBoKay1961a"/><citedRange>112, 121</citedRange></bibl>, also reports on the discovery and, on p. 115, provides an eye drawing of the inscription with Burmese transliteration. <bibl><ptr target="bib:Luce1985_01"/><citedRange>I, 146</citedRange></bibl>, gives an overview.</p>
